{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2f1641e1ee","title":"中央关于印发和组织学习三个镇反文件的通知","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e107b861ff","index":0,"year":1951,"month":2,"day":22,"articleId":"2f1641e1ee"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""},{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1322852cf9","type":"title","text":"中央关于印发和组织学习三个镇反文件的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2f1641e1ee"},{"id":"3dba4687fd","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2f1641e1ee"},{"id":"f8a04d67f0","type":"appellation","text":"各中央局，各大军区党委，并转分局，各省委，市委，区党委及师以上人民解放军党委：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2f1641e1ee"},{"id":"c398b6eca9","type":"paragraph","text":"中央人民政府已于二月二十一日颁布了惩治反革命条例，在二月二十二日的报纸上已发表了这个条例及彭真同志向中央人民政府委员会关于这个问题的报告，人民日报并写了《为什么必须坚决镇压反革命》的长篇社论，以上三个文件，请你们迅即印成一本，广泛发行，并组织干部及民主人士普遍地进行学习，务使镇压反革命问题在全党及全国人民中获得正确的了解，批评各种错误的思想，以达坚决彻底地镇压反革命的目的。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2f1641e1ee"},{"id":"2917d619fe","type":"paragraph","text":" 中央二月二十二日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2f1641e1ee"}],"page":{"id":"841a926333","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2f1641e1ee","start":0,"end":0}},"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"ab7eef11da","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"2f1641e1ee","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"彭真，当时任中共中央政治局委员、中央书记处候补书记、政务院政治法律委员会副主任。"}],"contents":[{"id":"2f8737ec9f","type":"paragraph","text":"中央人民政府已于二月二十一日颁布了惩治反革命条例，在二月二十